channel.title: I cant log in
channel.description:
ive been trying to make a server
Im very new at this and my skill with computers is basic, i followed more then one guide on this site so dont just tell me to go look at those.
basically i put in my name, password, and no-ip thing, and have my server thing saying " whatever its called is online"minimized, and i click log in, it logs in sometimes ( half the time it just freezes) but when it does log on im in for a split second then kicked back out to the login screen...
anyone know whats going on?
